Fig. 2. Multiple sequences in proPhoAS4 are bound by the DnaK SBD. The Ile401 and Ile438 region of 1H-13C-HMQC spectra of ILV-13CH3–labeled DnaK SBD in the presence of unlabeled, unfolded proPhoAS4 at low (Left) and high
