SBD at the same concentration is in SI Appendix, Fig. S12). The data in Fig. 7A make it clear that the picture described
above is not complete, as the 1H-13C-HMQC spectrum of ILV13CH3-SBD bound to proPhoAS4 reveals a set of strong Ile401 and Ile438 resonances (labeled “U”) and additional minor res-
